{"id":232709866,"title":"試營運到底在幹嘛？","content":"最近自己的店開了，開幕確切時間未定，先開門試賣\n\n試賣期間我只做來店消費全品項折10元，未貼布條、未發傳單、未做過多宣傳。WHY?\n\n試營運的目的是順流程、調整配方、擬定SOP，如果生意興隆是好事嗎？\n\nNO!\n\n你能把握出杯品質？能確定客人在服務上的感官是ok的？所以我覺得如果不是加盟體系在培訓期間就有營運經驗，那千萬不要草率地大肆宣傳。\n\n這幾天生意雖然不好，但的確更能掌握整體節奏以及發現問題。\n\nhttps://i.imgur.com/pImrAm2.jpg\nhttps://i.imgur.com/U7RFtNu.jpg","excerpt":"最近自己的店開了，開幕確切時間未定，先開門試賣，試賣期間我只做來店消費全品項折10元，未貼布條、未發傳單、未做過多宣傳。WHY？試營運的目的是順流程、調整配方、擬定SOP，如果生意興隆是好事嗎？NO！","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"6120536f-6a70-49bb-8891-ec0ba2f4b396","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-18T05:45:41.288Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-18T05:45:41.288Z","commentCount":1,"likeCount":34,"tags":[],"topics":["咖啡","創業","手沖咖啡","咖啡廳","精品咖啡"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"咖啡","forumAlias":"coffee","school":"老鼠會會長","department":"ciancoffee","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":34}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/pImrAm2.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/U7RFtNu.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"a230a774-cdd0-4428-ad9c-e2d98e159eb6","url":"https://i.imgur.com/pImrAm2l.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/pImrAm2l.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/pImrAm2l.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-18T05:45:41.288Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-18T05:45:41.288Z"},{"id":"a230a774-cdd0-4428-ad9c-e2d98e159eb6","url":"https://i.imgur.com/pImrAm2.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/pImrAm2","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/pImrAm2l.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-18T05:45:41.288Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-18T05:45:41.288Z"},{"id":"cf946530-d6dd-4ec9-bbaa-f9bac3c6af0a","url":"https://i.imgur.com/U7RFtNu.jpg","